The paper deals with secure middleboxes and encrypted traffic processing, which are topics related to computer security (cs.CR) and computer networks (cs.NI). The paper also discusses the use of cloud data centres for network function virtualisation (cs.DC) and proposes a new protocol for encrypted pattern matching (cs.SE). Finally, the paper addresses privacy concerns related to traffic redirection (cs.CY).
